Watts Water to Pay U.S. SEC $3.6 Million in Settlement Agreement

-- B y   J e r a n   W i t t e n s t e i n
-- 
2011-10-14T18:34:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/watts-water-to-pay-u-s-sec-3-6-million-in-settlement-agreement.html
Watts Water Technologies Inc. (WTS)  will
pay the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission $3.6 million to
settle claims that a former subsidiary violated the Foreign
Corrupt Practices Act, according to a regulatory filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeran Wittenstein at 
 jwittenstei1@bloomberg.net  